{
    "title": "Feature Release",
    "description": "End-to-end feature release playbook covering planning, development, testing, launch, and post-launch phases. Ensures coordinated releases across all teams.",
    "version": 1,
    "channel_name_template": "release-<name>",
    "message_on_join_enabled": true,
    "message_on_join": "**Feature Release Channel**\n\nThis channel coordinates all activities for this feature release.\n\n**Release Team:**\n- Product Manager: @[to be assigned]\n- Engineering Lead: @[to be assigned]\n- QA Lead: @[to be assigned]\n- Marketing: @[to be assigned]\n- Customer Success: @[to be assigned]\n\n**Key Dates:**\n- Target Release: [Date]\n- Code Freeze: [Date]\n- Beta Start: [Date]\n\n**Resources:**\n- PRD: [Link]\n- Design Specs: [Link]\n- Release Checklist: [Link]",
    "run_summary_template_enabled": true,
    "run_summary_template": "**Release Overview**\n\n**Feature Name:** \n**Version:** \n**Release Type:** (Major / Minor / Patch)\n\n**Key Dates:**\n- Development Start: \n- Code Freeze: \n- Beta/Staging: \n- Target Release: \n\n**Status:** (Planning / In Development / Testing / Ready / Released)\n\n**Team:**\n- PM: \n- Eng Lead: \n- QA Lead: \n\n**Risks/Blockers:**\n\n\n**Go/No-Go Decision:**",
    "status_update_enabled": true,
    "reminder_timer_default_seconds": 259200,
    "retrospective_enabled": true,
    "retrospective_reminder_interval_seconds": 604800,
    "retrospective_template": "### Release Summary\nBrief overview of what was released, key features, and overall success.\n\n### Metrics\n- On-time delivery: Yes / No (if no, days delayed: ___)\n- Bugs found in production: ___\n- Customer adoption (first week): ___%\n- Support tickets related to release: ___\n\n### What Went Well\n- Development process\n- Testing coverage\n- Communication\n- Launch execution\n\n### What Could Be Improved\n- Planning\n- Coordination\n- Testing\n- Documentation\n\n### Customer Feedback\n- Positive feedback:\n- Issues reported:\n- Feature requests:\n\n### Action Items\n| Action | Owner | Due Date |\n|--------|-------|----------|\n| | | |\n\n### Lessons for Next Release\nKey takeaways to apply to future releases.",
    "signal_any_keywords_enabled": true,
    "signal_any_keywords": [
        "feature release",
        "product launch",
        "go-live",
        "release ready",
        "shipping"
    ],
    "metrics": [],
    "checklists": [
